text: Kemoh Sidiki Kamara (born 3 July 1995) is a Liberian footballer who plays for Barrack Young Controllers, as a defender. ==Career== Born in Lassaou, Guinea, Kamara has played for Barrack Young Controllers. He made his international debut for Liberia in 2016. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Liberian footballers Category:Liberia international footballers Category:Barrack Young Controllers FC players Category:Association football defenders
